delete from ClientBalance
where (client_id, client_name, client_balance_date, client_balance_value) in (
select client_id, client_name, client_balance_date, client_balance_value
from ( select client_id, client_name, client_balance_date, client_balance_value,
ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by client_id, client_name, client_balance_date, client_balance_value
ORDER BY client_id) as rn
from ClientBalance )
t where t.rn > 1 );

Bu joyda dublikate elementlarni topib olamiz va 1 ta elementdan boshqa hamma elemnetni delete qilamiz va bizda 1 ta unique element qoladi.

Ikkinchi yoli ham bor qoshilayotganda tekshirib qoyish agar hamma columnlar unique bolsa birlashtirib unique constraint qoshib qoyish.